drive

Class GoogleDriveService

  • java.lang.Object
    • drive.GoogleDriveService

  • public class GoogleDriveService
extends java.lang.Object
    The GoogleDriveService is a Singleton class used to interface with Google Drive and Sheets. Future versions may get rid of the Google Sheets interface in favor of using CSV files to maximize versatility.
